# Medical Text Summarization Project Structure

src/
├── models/           # Model definitions and architectures
├── data/            # Data loading, preprocessing, and augmentation
├── training/        # Training loops and optimization
├── evaluation/      # Metrics and evaluation utilities
├── utils/           # General utilities and helpers
├── config/          # Configuration management
└── demo/            # Demo and visualization components

configs/             # YAML configuration files
data/               # Raw and processed datasets
scripts/            # Training and evaluation scripts
notebooks/          # Jupyter notebooks for exploration
tests/              # Unit and integration tests
assets/             # Generated artifacts and visualizations
demo/               # Streamlit/Gradio demo applications

